snippet.title: ED to Probe Bhajiyawala under Money Laundering Case

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Enforcement Directorate will probe Surat's Bhajiyawala under money laundering case. In a raid Income tax has recovered unaccounted money and property worth two thousand rupees from tea seller.
